table_description: This table contains information on user activity and engagement with the Fellow app on a snapshot date.
This table contains information on user activity and engagement in the past 1, 7, 14, 30, 60 days.
This table contains details on the user of the Fellow app.
This table contains details on the workspace of the Fellow app.
This table contains details on the customer information, which are the workspaces that have subscribed or is currently subscribed.
This table contains details on the complete subscription history of a workspace.
This table is the pivoted version of fct_monthly_recurring_revenue, with columns being the month number and entries being the mrr of the workspace.
This table contains list of dates and their information like year number, month number, etc.
